Class Shape<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • model.Shape<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Image, Line, Oval, Rectangle

    public abstract class Shape<E>
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    The shape object is the class that links to all shapes so NetPaintGUI doesn't know about them but still has the ability to draw a shape of that requested type.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
